<script>


var exchURL="";
var sectURL="";
var regURL="";
var mktcapURL="";

var exch = get_querystring_value("exchange");
var markt = get_querystring_value("market");


var sect = get_querystring_value("industry");


var reg = get_querystring_value("region");
var cntry = get_querystring_value("country");
var state = get_querystring_value("state");


var mktcap = get_querystring_value("marketcap");


function updateURL(anchor, paramlabel, paramvalue)
{
	//remove "all" parameters from querystring
	url = document.location.href.replace(/\?\S+=ALL$|&\S+=ALL/g,"").replace(/\?\S+=ALL&/,"?");

	//remove current paramlabel if one exists
	switch(paramlabel)
	{
		case "exchange":
			if(exch!=false)
				url = url.replace("exchange="+exch,"");
			if(markt!=false)
				url = url.replace("market="+markt,"");
			url = url.replace(/&{2,}/,"&").replace("?&","?").replace(/&$/,"").replace(/\?$/,"").replace("#","");
			break;

		case "region":
			if(reg!=false)
				url = url.replace("region="+reg,"");
			if(cntry!=false)
				url = url.replace("country="+cntry,"");
			if(state!=false)
				url = url.replace("state="+state,"");
			url = url.replace(/&{2,}/,"&").replace("?&","?").replace(/&$/,"").replace(/\?$/,"").replace("#","");
			break;

		case "industry":
			if(sect!=false)
				url = url.replace("industry="+sect,"").replace(/&{2,}/,"&").replace("?&","?").replace(/&$/,"").replace(/\?$/,"").replace("#","");
			break;

		case "marketcap":
			if(mktcap!=false)
				url = url.replace("marketcap="+mktcap,"").replace(/&{2,}/,"&").replace("?&","?").replace(/&$/,"").replace(/\?$/,"").replace("#","");
			break;

	}
	url = url+"&"+paramlabel+"="+paramvalue;
	url = url.replace(".aspx&",".aspx?").replace("?&","?");
	anchor.href = url;
}

	
</script>

<!-- START page bottom script -->
    <script type="text/javascript">
    $(document).ready(function () {
    setTimeout(function () {
        initStickyContent();
    }, 5000);
});

function initStickyContent() {
    var menuHeight = 85; //masthead height; padding between sticky content and top of the screen
    var bottomElementSelector = '#footerAd';//bottom boundary element which sticky content won't move past vertically
    var footerOffset = 0; //padding between sticky content and bottom boundary element
    var content1Selector = '#sticky-container1';//initial sticky element
    var content1Height = 411;//height of initial sticky element

    function initStickyContent1() {
        var stickyContainer = $(content1Selector);
        if (stickyContainer.length == 0) return;
        var stickyTop = stickyContainer.offset().top - menuHeight;
        var maxBottom = $(bottomElementSelector).offset().top - footerOffset;
        //define scroll distance, bottom point is based on scroll distance            
        var bottom = $(bottomElementSelector).offset().top - footerOffset - content1Height - menuHeight - 600;
        //if scroll distance goes into footer, readjust
        if (bottom > maxBottom) bottom = maxBottom;
        var currentlyStickied = false;
        var disableSticky = false;
        var distance = bottom - stickyTop - content1Height - menuHeight;
        $(window).scroll(function () {
            var windowTop;
            if (!disableSticky) {
                windowTop = $(window).scrollTop();
                if (stickyTop < windowTop) {
                    if (windowTop < bottom) {
                        if (!currentlyStickied) {
                            //scroll position is past sticky point but above bottom point and content is currently non-sticky
                            //go from non-sticky to sticky
                            stickyContainer.css({ position: 'fixed', top: menuHeight + "px" });
                            currentlyStickied = true;
                        }
                    }
                    else {
                        if (currentlyStickied) {
                            //scroll position is past sticky point and past bottom point and content is currently sticky
                            //go from sticky to original position and disable future stickiness
                            stickyContainer.css({ position: 'fixed', top: (menuHeight - 860) + "px" });
                            currentlyStickied = false;
                        }
                    }
                }
                else {
                    if (currentlyStickied) {
                        //scroll position is above sticky point but content is currently sticky
                        //go from sticky to original position
                        stickyContainer.css('position', 'static');
                        currentlyStickied = false;
                    }
                }
            }
        });
    }

    initStickyContent1();
}
</script>
<!-- END page bottom script -->
